data.description: Welcome to 1317 Dunbarton Ct, Kissimmee, FL 34758! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home with a 2-car garage offers a perfect blend of modern features and comfort. The spacious kitchen boasts an oversized granite countertop island, 30-inch cabinets, and top-of-the-line GE stainless steel appliances, including a refrigerator, range, microwave, and dishwasher. The open split floor plan allows for seamless flow, and you'll find the master suite thoughtfully positioned on a separate side of the home for added privacy. The master bathroom is a retreat with a garden tub, stand-in shower, and walk-in closet. This home includes solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency. All bedrooms feature vinyl floors, closets, and fans for convenience and comfort. The bathrooms impress with single sinks and granite countertops. Step into the backyard oasis, which includes two sheds, various fruit trees, and a serene conservation area. Enjoy outdoor gatherings in the enclosed lanai and gazebo, surrounded by a beautiful vinyl fence. Don't miss the chance to make it yours and embrace a lifestyle of comfort, style, and serenity in this sought-after location. Schedule a viewing today and experience the delights of 1317 Dunbarton Ct!
